category: Math
requires: libgcc1 libreadline6
sdesc: "Console unit convertor"
ldesc: "The Units program converts quantities expressed in various 
scales to their equivalents in other scales. The units program can 
handle multiplicative scale changes as well as nonlinear conversions 
such as Fahrenheit to Celsius or wire gauge. Units comes with an 
annotated, extendable database defining over two thousand units."
